                        h2 Tips for Building a Budget-Friendly Home Gym
                        p Here are some strategies for setting up a home gym on a budget:
                        ul
                            li 
                                strong Start with Basics:
                                |  Begin with essential equipment like dumbbells, resistance bands, and a yoga mat.
