                                strong Shop Second-Hand:
                                |  Look for used equipment on online marketplaces or at garage sales.
                            li 
                                strong Focus on Bodyweight Exercises:
                                |  Bodyweight exercises can be highly effective and require little to no equipment.
                            li 
                                strong Create a Dedicated Space:
                                |  Designate a specific area in your home for your workouts to keep your equipment organized.
                        p With these tips, you can set up a home gym that meets your fitness needs without a large investment.
