                        p Here are some key benefits of incorporating walking into your routine:
                        ul
                            li 
                                strong Accessible Exercise:
                                |  Walking is easy to do and requires no special equipment.
                            li 
                                strong Improves Cardiovascular Health:
                                |  Regular walking can enhance heart health and reduce the risk of cardiovascular diseases.
                            li 
                                strong Supports Weight Management:
